Requirements
~~~~~~~~~~~~

*Note*: probably incomplete.

* Python 2.7 
* for TTS one or more of:
  - MaryTTS, py-marytts
  - espeak-ng, py-espeak-ng
  - SVOX Pico TTS, py-picotts
* for ASR
  - kaldi-asr 5.4.248, py-kaldi-asr
* sequitur
* pulseaudio
* webrtc

